Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch

Class BatchFactory

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.batch.BatchFactory
public class BatchFactory extends Object
BatchFactory provides a Builder to create a Batch instance with download requests along with a file; which you can use with this factory's load(java.io.File) method to load a Batch instance in the state it concluded last time executed.
Since:
1.0
